Titolo: GTR – FIA GT Racing Game

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: GTR – FIA GT Racing Game is a sports car racing simulator developed by SimBin Studios (later Sector3 Studios) for the x86 PC. Simbin has also released an "add-on pack" called "Kings of Ovals" which contains a set of new oval-style tracks. A sequel, GTR 2 – FIA GT Racing Game, was released in 2006.

Genere: Sim racing

Valutazione: 85
